Class DateValidator

java.lang.Object
  edu.umn.se.trap.rules.input.InputValidationRule

All Implemented Interfaces:
TRAPRule
public class DateValidator
extends InputValidationRule

Check that arrival and departure datetimes come in the correct order. Check that the reported number of days corresponds with the length between the departure and arrival datetimes (inclusive). Check that the trip arrival time is before the submission time for the trip.
